# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

## [0.0.1] - 2026-07-01 — Initial release

### Added
- Types: integer, boolean, list
- Pattern matching with guards
- List construction and splat operators
- Tail-call elimination
- Built-in arithmetic, logical, bitwise, and shift operators
- `count_trailing_zeros` operator
- CLI interface for running ReWrite programs
- Example programs: factorial, listn, nprime, nqueens (two versions)
